### Flask DB API - Health

GET http://localhost:5000/health


### Listar tablas

GET http://localhost:5000/db/tables?db=dev.db


### Esquema de una tabla (ejemplo: users)

GET http://localhost:5000/db/table_schema?tabla=users&db=dev.db


### Leer registros (todas las columnas)

GET http://localhost:5000/db/read?tabla=users&campos=*&db=dev.db


### Insertar registro
POST http://localhost:5000/db/insert
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tabla": "users",
  "valores": {
    "email": "user{{$timestamp}}@example.com",
    "password": "1234567"
  },
  "db": "dev.db"
}


### Actualizar registro(s)
POST http://localhost:5000/db/update
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tabla": "users",
  "campo": "password",
  "valor": "abc12345",
  "condicion_sql": "email LIKE 'user%@example.com'",
  "db": "dev.db"
}


### Borrar por PK (id)
POST http://localhost:5000/db/delete_pk
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tabla": "users",
  "pk": "id",
  "valor": 1,
  "db": "dev.db"
}


